          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Should I include software and salaries in CPA?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>For channel-level CPA, no — only include ad spend. For CAC or true business CPA, yes — include ad platform fees, marketing software, agency retainers, and the fully loaded salary of anyone whose time contributed. Counting only ad spend flatters the number.</p></div></div>
